==Korean==
===Noun===
'''구멍''' gumeong
#[[hole]]
#:바지에 '''구멍'''이 났다. (''baji-e gumeong-i nattda'') [I] got a hole in my trousers. (Literally "A hole appeared in my trousers.")
#:벽에 '''구멍'''을 뚫다. (''byeog-e '''gumeong'''eul ddulta'') Drill a '''hole''' in a wall. 

